peopleAlsoAsk.question: What is the best way to sell antique clocks?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: If you are interested in selling your clock, good online platforms to try include Chairish, Ebay, Poshmark, Facebook Marketplace, and Ruby Lane. Alternately, you can consider a yard sale, an antique or flea market in your local area, or a consignment shop.

peopleAlsoAsk.question: Does anyone buy antique clocks?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: People collect antique clocks for their beauty, craftsmanship, historical and scientific significance. Many antique buyers choose them for their decorative appeal or fascinating inner workings.
